    "statementHTML": "<div class=\"statement-body\">\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-goal\">\n   <h2><span class=\"icon icon-goal\">&nbsp;</span><span>Goal </span></h2>\n   <span class=\"question-statement\">Given a number as a string of digits <var>s</var>, replacing each digit with its mirror equivalent.<br><br>The mirror is obtained by:<br>1. Reversing the digits .<br>2. Replacing each digit with it's mirror equivalent.<br><pre style=\"font-family: monospace\"></pre><pre style=\"font-family: monospace\"><br>Mirror map:<br>| Digit | Mirror |<br>| ----- | ------ |<br>| 0     | 0      |<br>| 1     | 1      |<br>| 2     | 5      |<br>| 5     | 2      |<br>| 6     | 9      |<br>| 8     | 8      |<br>| 9     | 6      |<br></pre><pre style=\"font-family: monospace\"></pre><br>An invalid digit is any digit not present in the mirror map above <strong>(specifically: 3, 4, and 7)</strong>. If the input string contains any invalid digit, output <const>INVALID</const>.</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-protocol\">\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-input\"><strong>Line 1: </strong>A string <var>s</var> representing a sequence of digits.</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-output\">The mirrored number or <const>INVALID</const>.</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Constraints</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-constraints\">1 &le; length of <var>s</var> &le; 256</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Example</div>\n      <div class=\"statement-inout\">\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-in\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-in\">2</pre>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-out\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-out\">5</pre>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n   </div>\n</div>"
